# Creator Foundation вҖ” Architecture Review

**Task:** 2025-12-16__CREATOR-FOUNDATION  
**Owner:** Engineering Lead Agent  
**Status:** вң… APPROVED  
**Date:** 2025-12-16

---

## 1. Goals & Scope

### Primary Goals
1. Enable users to apply to become creators
2. Integrate Veriff for KYC identity verification
3. Integrate Square for payment processing
4. Provide creator dashboard with basic metrics

### Assumptions
- User has verified email before applying
- Age verification passed (18+)
- US/UK/EU regions only initially

