## 3. API Endpoints

### 3.1 Creator Application

| Endpoint | Method | Description | Auth |
|----------|--------|-------------|------|
| `/api/creator/apply` | POST | Submit creator application | Required |
| `/api/creator/status` | GET | Get application/KYC status | Required |

**POST /api/creator/apply**
```typescript
// Request
{
  displayName: string;
  bio: string;
  categoryId: string;
  subscriptionPrice: number; // 4.99 - 49.99
}

// Response 201
{
  creatorProfileId: string;
  status: 'pending_kyc';
  nextStep: '/creator/verify';
}
```

### 3.2 KYC Verification (Veriff)

| Endpoint | Method | Description | Auth |
|----------|--------|-------------|------|
| `/api/creator/kyc/start` | POST | Create Veriff session | Required |
| `/api/creator/kyc/status` | GET | Check KYC status | Required |
| `/api/webhooks/veriff` | POST | Veriff callback | HMAC |

**POST /api/creator/kyc/start**
```typescript
// Response 200
{
  sessionUrl: string;  // Veriff hosted flow URL
  sessionId: string;
}
```

**POST /api/webhooks/veriff** (Webhook)
```typescript
// Veriff sends decision webhook
// Verify HMAC signature before processing
// Update creator_profiles.kyc_status
```

### 3.3 Square Payments

| Endpoint | Method | Description | Auth |
|----------|--------|-------------|------|
| `/api/creator/square/connect` | GET | Start Square OAuth | Required |
| `/api/creator/square/callback` | GET | OAuth callback | State token |
| `/api/creator/payouts` | GET | Get payout history | Required |
| `/api/creator/payouts/settings` | PATCH | Update payout settings | Required |

**GET /api/creator/square/connect**
```typescript
// Response 302 Redirect to Square OAuth URL
// State token stored in session for CSRF protection
```

### 3.4 Creator Profile

| Endpoint | Method | Description | Auth |
|----------|--------|-------------|------|
| `/api/creator/profile` | GET | Get own creator profile | Required |
| `/api/creator/profile` | PATCH | Update creator profile | Required |
| `/api/creator/subscription` | PATCH | Update pricing | Required |
| `/api/public/creator/[handle]` | GET | Public creator profile | None |

